  "description": "A working procedure for analyzing a specific wellness practice as an instance of californication: identify the structural contradiction it metabolizes, map the genre, identify the feedback loops, locate where the metabolism lands, note what the practice admits and refuses. Structural, not a moral verdict on the practice or practitioner.",
  "name": "How to Read a Wellness Practice as Californication",
